EscapeHatchLeaveCandidateSetTest
├── given caller status is not EXITING
│   └── it should revert {EscapeHatch__InvalidStatus}
└── given caller status is EXITING
    ├── when exitableAt has not been reached
    │   └── it should revert {EscapeHatch__NotExitableYet}
    └── when exitableAt has been reached
        ├── given caller was not punished
        │   ├── it should delete candidate data
        │   ├── it should transfer correct refund to caller
        │   └── it should emit CandidateExited event
        └── given caller was punished
            ├── it should delete candidate data
            ├── it should transfer correct refund to caller
            └── it should emit CandidateExited event
